## Documentation-Driven Development

### Core Principle
> Documentation is AI memory. Everything the AI needs to know must exist in files it can read.

### Documentation Hierarchy
1. **CLAUDE.md** - Project overview (read first, always)
2. **Context.md** - Documentation index
3. **Session.md** - Current state (dynamic)
4. **Tasks.md** - What needs doing
5. **Supporting docs** - As needed

### Documentation Maintenance
- Update Session.md every session
- Review CLAUDE.md monthly
- Keep Context.md current with doc changes
- Archive outdated documentation

