## Best Practices

### Do's
- ✅ Always load context before starting work
- ✅ Update Session.md before ending sessions
- ✅ Document decisions with rationale
- ✅ Use consistent patterns across codebase
- ✅ Review AI-generated code before committing
- ✅ Break large tasks into smaller, trackable items
- ✅ Maintain audit trail in Prompt_History
- ✅ Test changes before deployment

### Don'ts
- ❌ Don't skip context loading
- ❌ Don't make architectural changes without documentation
- ❌ Don't deploy without testing
- ❌ Don't let documentation become stale
- ❌ Don't assume AI remembers previous sessions
- ❌ Don't make security-sensitive changes without review
- ❌ Don't skip the session end update

